    doi: 10.1364/OE.25.015131
    notes: "Implemented by rgb_to_jzazbz() and rgb_to_jzczhz()."
  - type: generic
    title: "A perceptual color space for image processing"
    authors:
      - family-names: Ottosson
        given-names: Björn
    year: 2020
    url: "https://bottosson.github.io/posts/oklab/"
    notes: "Implemented by rgb_to_oklab() and oklab_to_rgb()."
  - type: software
    title: "GeoPalette — the Python implementation of the same conversions"
    authors:
      - family-names: Pawelec
        given-names: Igor
    url: "https://github.com/igorpawelec/GeoPalette"
    notes: >-
      Agreement is measured rather than exact: GeoPalette stores intermediates
      in single precision where R has only double, so the two agree to better
      than 1.7e-6 of each component's range. See ?GeoPaletteR-agreement.
